channel.title: Can't get your server online?
channel.description:
For you people who still can't get there server online and tryed everything possiable and still get get it up?
Well i have one question for you...
What is your internet provider?
IF is any kind of satellite internet like HUGHES NET you can't run a server due to there gay firewall.
HOW i know this...i had hughes net, i tryed to run a private server, it doesn't work... I even called hughes net support and they say you can't because of the build-in Firewall.
I hope i helped some people
please post if you have a satellite internet and you host a server and it works...i would like to know what you did.
(i don't need help running a server FYI, this post was to help people know what they can't run a server on Hughes net...)
